Class Coin

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.StoreObject
      • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.Coin

  • public class Coin
extends StoreObject
    This object stores the weight and value of each type of Coin, and hence enables the machine to recognize each Coin entered.

    Author:
    Olivo Miotto, Pang Ping Li
